Constructor Detail

SafeDepositAgent

public SafeDepositAgent(Console console,
                        SafeDepositMessage message,
                        java.lang.String[] nodesToContact,
                        int groupSize,
                        long responseTimeout,
                        long withdrawalTimeout,
                        boolean verbose)
Parameters:
console - A console configured to communicate with a running cluster.
message - The message that builds contents for deposit.
nodesToContact - The directly contacted node groups or nodes on which deposits will be made.
groupSize - Number of nodes to contact at once. (3 is usually good.)
responseTimeout - Millis to wait for each response. This needs to be long enough to allow the message to be sent and all data streaming back to be received. Note that each node to contact will be given this amount of time serially.
withdrawalTimeout - Millis to wait for withdrawals before giving up.
